{"tid":1839754,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"全城中伏！！中共想賴啲賤畜食野味，Spin走武漢P4實驗室輸出病毒","createTime":"2020-01-24T14:39:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-01T13:06:23.000Z","uid":30510,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"0e8c383bfbe51cd54e7b06c7bbeb3ca62d275a3b","tid":1839754,"uid":30510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T14:39:02.000Z","msg":"英國《每日郵報》1月23日報導，中共在武漢建置實驗室，用來研究SARS和伊波拉病毒；<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">美國生物安全專家2017年就警告，病毒可能會「逃脫」，該設施已成為應對爆發的關鍵。武漢國家生物安全實驗室，距離華南海鮮市場約20英里的地方，有些人想知道，這次疫情爆發的震央中心是否巧合。此外，《自然》2017年2月引述專家的質疑，中方不需1座以上BSL-4實驗室；過剩能力，恐被認為可用來開發生物武器</span></span>。"},{"pid":"09834d9429477b14aece290a54bd9b7cd2505f08","tid":1839754,"uid":276716,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T14:41:43.000Z","msg":"分析點解今次可能係實驗室事故<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1839243/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1839243/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"35df7e0dfd966192e3407c85b0c3ecf4e8737049","tid":1839754,"uid":247817,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T14:46:22.000Z","msg":"太撚多巧合，p4係武漢，而爆疫症又係武漢，重要好似話唔俾病毒樣本其他國定研究<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個人覺得人造可能性都好撚大"},{"pid":"8a105a3f75befc6830812ef1a19206562d19f7bf","tid":1839754,"uid":30976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T15:14:43.000Z","msg":"十二月果陣好似仲有支那網民拎果個實驗塞打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有冇果張圖"},{"pid":"3ab7bfa05726be6c4b659b078c5acf03ad983d5a","tid":1839754,"uid":41545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a105a3f75befc6830812ef1a19206562d19f7bf","tid":1839754,"uid":30976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T15:14:43.000Z","msg":"十二月果陣好似仲有支那網民拎果個實驗塞打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有冇果張圖"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T15:21:41.000Z","msg":"同求"},{"pid":"f1209d1dcf9af8858a81d0a4086974de